{"tid":1544211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆搵仔+革命手冊channel呼籲：騎劫「曱甴」稱號，叫返警察做曱甴","createTime":"2019-09-05T13:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:09:06.000Z","uid":131691,"like":45,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f56b751259b9c03ae146db418139a9f887608304","tid":1544211,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔：<br />\n<br />\n&lt;論騎劫的重要性&gt; <br />\n大家都知道搵仔channel最先係由對家發起嘅 <br />\n自從有咗我哋越玩越大之後<br />\n最近有人pm我哋話對家抄襲我哋<br />\n真係笑死我<br />\n完全騎劫成功 <br />\n<br />\n所以大家下一步可以嘗試騎劫&rsquo;曱甴&rsquo;呢個稱號<br />\n見到狗就嗌佢哋曱甴<br />\n返學見到狗仔都嗌佢哋曱甴仔<br />\n盡快騎劫&rsquo;曱甴&rsquo;呢個稱號<br />\n令對面所有&rsquo;曱甴&rsquo;文宣失效<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Dadfindboy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDadfindboy&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=cc6f5db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dadfindboy</a><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n革命手冊：<br />\n<br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲我地叫返黑警做曱甴<br />\n騎劫稱呼<br />\n不如由而家開始<br />\n將狗=曱甴<br />\n普通軍裝=普通曱甴<br />\n防暴=綠色曱甴<br />\n速龍=藍色曱甴<br />\n臥底=黃色曱甴(包括記者，first aid，前線，路人，保安等等)<br />\n白衫=白色曱甴<br />\n公安/解放軍混警=紅色曱甴<br />\n警察記招=曱甴記招<br />\nEU=曱甴車<br />\n籠車/旅巴=大曱甴車<br />\n私家車=細曱甴車<br />\n警署=曱甴屋<br />\n引龜=引曱甴<br />\n開槍=曱甴痾屎<br />\n開始清場=小心飛曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ResistBasics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FResistBasics&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=4296445d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ResistBasics</a>"},{"pid":"9fc0b924deada44035cd9f9f20a24aa1b08a10f7","tid":1544211,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c51e40433f292ca04a2cbafe8b8aa962e96d0ab","tid":1544211,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"441154a6257bb858f47c872e4e780a1522acc98f","tid":1544211,"uid":129622,"like":